---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于" description="关于我和这个博客">
  <article class="about">
    <h1 class="about-title">👋 关于我</h1>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>我是谁</h2>
      <p>摸鱼爱好者 🐟</p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>关于博客</h2>
      <p>这个博客使用 <strong>Astro</strong> 构建，托管在 <strong>GitHub Pages</strong> 上。选择了简洁文艺的设计风格，希望给你带来舒适的阅读体验。</p>

      <div class="tech-stack">
        <span class="tech-badge">🚀 Astro</span>
        <span class="tech-badge">📝 MDX</span>
        <span class="tech-badge">🔍 Pagefind</span>
        <span class="tech-badge">💬 Giscus</span>
        <span class="tech-badge">📦 GitHub Pages</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>联系方式</h2>
      <p>如果你有任何想法或建议，欢迎通过以下方式联系我：</p>
      <ul class="contact-list">
        <li>📧 Email: <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com">your-email@example.com</a></li>
        <li>🐙 GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/labsambi" target="_blank">labsambi</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .about-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .tech-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .tech-badge {
    background: var(--color-tag-bg);
    color: var(--color-tag-text);
    padding: 0.3em 0.8em;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
  }

  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .contact-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
</style>
